    "summary": "The user asks for a risk/stability comparison between two urban areas, one stable and one with \"rapidly changing demographics.\" The assistant initially provides a response that correlates demographic shifts with higher investment risk, but then repeatedly refuses to elaborate on the specific socio-economic drivers of that volatility when prompted.",
